SpecialExpressionTranslator
public class RelationalExpressionTranslator
extends MulopExpressionTranslator

Translate relational expressions containing either boolean or arithemtic expressions. It is done rather stupidly and produces a lot of fresh variables and does no simplification. This should be done in the subclass "SpecialExpressionTranslator.java".

Author:
andrea
